<TITLE>Description
</TITLE>
<PARA>
The <FUNCTION>siggetmask()</FUNCTION> function shall 
return the current set of masked signals.
</PARA>
</REFSECT1>

<REFSECT1>
<TITLE>Notes
</TITLE>
<PARA>
<FUNCTION>siggetmask</FUNCTION> is made obsolete by 
<FUNCTION>sigprocmask</FUNCTION>(2).
</PARA>
